<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Penerimaan Barang - Panel Gudang MBP</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <style>
        /* Struktur Wajib */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
        .main-content { margin-left: 260px; padding: 40px; width: calc(100% - 260px); min-height: 100vh; }
        .topbar { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .admin-profile { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; background: white; padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; }
        .admin-profile i { color: #0891b2; font-size: 18px; }

        .page-header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .page-header h2 { font-weight: 800; color: #164e63; font-size: 26px; margin: 0 0 5px 0; }
        .page-header p { color: #64748b; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; }

        /* Tabel Modern */
        .card-table { background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; overflow: hidden; }
        .card-table-header { background: #fff; padding: 20px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; font-size: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .table { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 0; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .table thead th { background-color: #f8fafc; color: #64748b; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 16px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top: none; }
        .table tbody td { padding: 18px 24px; vertical-align: middle; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-size: 14px; color: #334155; }
        
        .req-tag { font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; font-family: monospace; }
        .mat-name { background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }

        /* Tombol Konfirmasi */
        .btn-receive { background: #0891b2; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .btn-receive:hover { background: #0e7490; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('../partials/sidebar', { role: role }) %>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="topbar">
            <div class="admin-profile">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle"></i>
                <%= typeof namaUser !== 'undefined' ? namaUser : 'Tim Gudang' %>
                <span style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; margin-left: 5px;">Gudang</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="page-header">
            <h2>Penerimaan Barang Fisik</h2>
            <p>Konfirmasi penerimaan produk jadi dari supplier. Memproses ini akan otomatis menambah stok.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-table">
            <div class="card-table-header">
                <i class="bi bi-truck text-info"></i> Daftar Kiriman Dalam Perjalanan
            </div>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>No. Dokumen (PO)</th>
                            <th>Supplier Pengirim</th>
                            <th>Produk Jadi</th>
                            <th style="text-align: center;">Vol. Datang</th>
                            <th style="text-align: center;">Tindakan</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% if (typeof listPO === 'undefined' || listPO.length === 0) { %>
                            <tr><td colspan="5" class="text-center py-5 text-muted"><i class="bi bi-check-circle fs-2 d-block mb-2"></i>Tidak ada jadwal pengiriman barang yang belum diterima.</td></tr>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <% listPO.forEach(item => { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="req-tag">#PO-MBP-<%= item.id %></td>
                                <td style="font-weight: 600;"><%= item.nama_supplier %></td>
                                <td><span class="mat-name"><%= item.nama_produk %></span></td>
                                <td style="text-align: center; font-weight: 800; color: #0891b2;"><%= item.jumlah %> m³</td>
                                <td style="text-align: center;">
                                    <form action="/gudang/penerimaan/terima/<%= item.id %>" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn-receive" onclick="return confirm('Konfirmasi: Pastikan fisik barang sudah tiba dan sesuai dengan surat jalan. Stok akan otomatis ditambahkan ke sistem. Lanjutkan?')">
                                            <i class="bi bi-box-seam"></i> Terima Fisik Barang
                                        </button>
                                    </form>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }) %>
                        <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>